attributes.review:
I downloaded this app to get a view at today’s politics but I couldn’t even enter the app! First I tried to enter but it bugged out on me and crashed. After 1,273,630,728,283,001 attempts I finally opened the app. But the load time was devastating as it took about 47 whole days for it to load and ask for registration. Now I’m not one to just register for anything, I only give my email to important places like Nike, Whole Foods, Walmart, Target, GameStop, Books a Million, Club Penguin, Buzzfeed, Youtube, Twitter, That one guy who asked for my email on the street, Zynn, Snapchat, Chase, SoundCloud, and others. But I wouldn’t DARE to give my email AND phone number to some ‘president’(?) so I couldn’t even explore the app. So Anyways 👁👄👁
                                                   \__🍜’\__/
